n\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104noh1665702742459.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/noh1665702742459.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/noh1665702742459.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"noh1665702742459\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Instructs the WRD that user authorization is required. If not specified, the web\n      server determines whether, and what kind of, user authorization is performed.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"noh1665702742459__topic_d147338e1_d147339e1_d147340e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"noh1665702742459__p_d147341e1_d147342e1_d147343e1\">AUTHORIZATION\n         </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"noh1665702742459__p_d147344e1_d147345e1_d147346e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">AUTHORIZATION</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">REMOTE_USER</code> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">Realm</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-value&gt;\n &lt;/init-param&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"noh1665702742459__p_d147347e1_d147348e1_d147349e1\">Default if omitted: determined by web server.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"noh1665702742459__section_fws_33g_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d730740e82\">Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"noh1665702742459__ul_nbv_j3g_xvb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"noh1665702742459__li_d51170e1_d51171e1_d51172e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">REMOTE_USER</code>—specifies that the web server should perform the\n               authentication (anonymous is not accepted). The web server identifies the remote user\n               and makes the user name known to the WRD to pass to the Uniface Server.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"noh1665702742459__li_d51173e1_d51174e1_d51175e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"noh1665702742459__p_d147353e1_d147354e1_d147355e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Realm</var>—name of the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Realm</var> in which the user is\n                  allowed to request web pages. BASIC authentication is performed by the web\n                  server.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"noh1665702742459__p_d147356e1_d147357e1_d147358e1\">The first time a user makes a request, the\n                  servlet instructs the browser to ask for a user ID and password, which are passed\n                  to the Uniface Server. If verifies the combination and if it succeeds, the user\n                  can request pages in this realm.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vqq1665702865300.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Using Web Server Authentication</a><p>If AUTHORIZATION=REMOTE_USER, the web server needs to perform the authentication, and anonymous is not allowed. You need to configure the web server to perform the authentication, and you can access the user logon information with $user and $password.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jon1665702865162.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Using Uniface Authentication</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fbm1665702669458.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Authentication for Uniface Web Applications</a><p>When developing a web application, you need to consider how to protect the web side from unauthorized access, virus attack, information theft, and so on. The first line of defence is authentication.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530360\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530360\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "AUTHORIZATION Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Instructs the WRD that user authorization is required. If not specified, the web server determines whether, and what kind of, user authorization is performed. AUTHORIZATION <init-param> <param-name> AUTHORIZATION </param-name> <param-value> REMOTE_USER | Realm </param-value> </init-param> Default if omitted: determined by web server. Values REMOTE_USER —specifies that the web server should perform the authentication (anonymous is not accepted). The web server identifies the remote user and makes the user name known to the WRD to pass to the Uniface Server. Realm —name of the Realm in which the user is allowed to request web pages. BASIC authentication is performed by the web server. The first time a user makes a request, the servlet instructs the browser to ask for a user ID and password, which are passed to the Uniface Server. If verifies the combination and if it succeeds, the user can request pages in this realm. Related Links Using Web Server Authentication If AUTHORIZATION=REMOTE_USER, the web server needs to perform the authentication, and anonymous is not allowed. You need to configure the web server to perform the authentication, and you can access the user logon information with $user and $password. Using Uniface Authentication Authentication for Uniface Web Applications When developing a web application, you need to consider how to protect the web side from unauthorized access, virus attack, information theft, and so on. The first line of defence is authentication. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}